name: Warning Contains Teeth
description:
Warning: Contains Teeth

A long time ago there was an extremely cursed Bitsy Jam.  So I started making this game which wildly scoped out of control.  I've come too far to commit this to a graveyard, so I made some finish touches and releasing this as is! Anyways here is the story for my now finished "Teeth" jam game.

Play as Agent 601D as he dives into the ruins of human civilization to find something to help fight off the Great Destroyer Whale MKIV before it eradicates all life!

Adam Le Doux - For making Bitsy in the first place! 

Ayolland - For Borksy, your one stop shop for implementing Bitsy hacks with ease!

Ruin - For the Image to Bitsy tool when enables me to do what I do. 

This fish for existing (WARNING THE LINK DOES CONTAIN TEEETH)
